column5: I took Fishhunter (Lloyd) up on the offer he posted last week for fishing on Bay of Quinte on Sunday.  It was one of the best days of fishing I've ever had!  Me with the catch of the day:  a 27 inch walleyeâ€¦ my best yet:  http://img128.imageshack.us/my.php?image=sany0006yv8.jpg   The day's catch, 7 pickerel total with an average size of around 4-5 pounds, and 4 very happy fishermen:  http://img232.imageshack.us/my.php?image=sany0010hu5.jpg  Thanks a lot to Lloyd for the outing on his boat.  It was a great day out.  Thanks also for all the tips on fishing in the Ottawa area!
Great day on the bay guys !!!!   some very nice walleyes...cheers
Very nice wallys.  Thanks for sharing.
Those are some nice eyes Lloyd knows how to put you on the fish  Rob
You boys did well, gotta like it...
Great report and pics auscanman  Congratulation on your PB     Super nice eyes Thanks for sharing Leechman
Nice catch on BOQ Glad to hear some fish are biting
